=Description=


"Naked Conversations is one of those books that you can't go 15 minutes in the blogosphere without triping over. Coauthored by Shel Israel and Robert Scoble, it gives some great advice to bloggers new and old. 

For my 54th podcast interview, I tracked down Shel Israel to hear his side of the story of writing it and pick his brain about marketing/pr in the social media age."
